data.title: NOLA Pickle Fest
data.meta_description: The pickleball tournament returns with divisions for various skill levels for men’s, women’s and mixed doubles and brackets for open competition and 40 years old and up. The event also features music by Bag of Donuts, DJs, parties, food trucks, vendors, raffles and a silent auction. At Mardi Gras World Wednesday, Aug. 7, through Sunday, Aug. 11. The event is organized by the Brees Dream Foundation.
